'''飓风希梅纳'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Jimena}}）是[[2003年太平洋飓风季|2003年太平洋飓风季]]第十场获命名的风暴和第二场飓风，于8月28日在远离陆地的[[太平洋|太平洋]]成为热带低气压，然后向西移动并快速增强，次日就达到飓风标准。风暴继续向西进入中太平洋，强度也持续提升，达到的最高强度在[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风标准，此后气旋就因[[风切变|风切变]]增多开始减弱。希梅纳从[[夏威夷群岛|夏威夷群岛]]南部上空掠过，于9月3日降级成热带低气压。风暴继续弱化，最终在穿越[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]后于9月5日逐渐消散，是有纪录以来少有的几场穿越[[西经140度线|西经140度]]和国际日期变更线的热带气旋之一。

希梅纳是[[2000年太平洋飓风季|2000年]]的飓风丹尼尔过后首场威胁[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]的[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋飓风]]<ref name="cphc">{{cite report | author1 = Andy Nash | author2 = Tim Craig | author3 = Robert Farell | author4 = Hans Rosendal | year = 2004 | title = 2003 Central North Pacific Tropical Cyclones | publisher = National Weather Service-Central Pacific Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2003.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211538/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2003.php | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。不过，气旋最终大幅减弱后从夏威夷群岛南部经过，由此构成的影响很小，也没有报导表明风暴曾导致人员伤亡。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Jimena 2003 track.png}}
2003年8月26日，东太平洋有扰动天气区形成并向西面飘移。这片扰动天气接下来开始组织，于8月28日成为第十{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="nhc">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimena Tropical Cyclone Report Report | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002014658/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP102003_Jimena.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP102003_Jimena.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。气旋继续西进，进入[[海面温度|水温]]超过28[[摄氏度|°C]]的海域并快速增强<ref>{{cite report | author = James Franklin | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Depression Ten-E Discussion Number #2 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.002.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312050329/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.002.shtml | date =  }}</ref>，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]很快就将之升级成热带风暴，并以“希梅纳”（{{lang|en|Jimena}}）命名<ref name="nhc" />。

风暴继续在向西前进的同时增强，8月29日的卫星图像显示希梅纳内部发展出层次分明的[[风眼|风眼]]，风速也提升到每小时97公里<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Beven | author2 = Knabb | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Jimena Discussion #5 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171627/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.005.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>，气旋接下来在当晚升级成飓风<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Alvia | author2 = Roberts | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimena Discussion #6 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307215213/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.006.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]下午15点，可视卫星图像显示，正朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动的风暴风眼内已有云层填充，中心以南还在逐渐发展出[[雨带|带状特征]]<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Alvia | author2 = Roberts | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimena Discussion #7 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-31 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/ep102003.discus.007.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。气旋逼近中太平洋盆地，于8月30日达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时165公里，最低[[气压|气压]]970[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.64[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="nhc" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点，美国国家飓风中心发布针对希梅纳的最后一份公告，因为飓风已穿越[[西经140度线|西经140度]]进入中太平洋飓风中心预警范围<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Beven | author2 = Knabb | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimena Forecast Advisory #9 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312051408/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/mar/ep102003.fstadv.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/mar/ep102003.fstadv.009.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。

[[File:Jimenavis2003.GIF|right]]

8月31日，气旋因遇到强烈的南向[[风切变|风切变]]而快速减弱，到9月1日强度已回落至热带风暴标准<ref name="cphc" />。风暴接下来转向[[罗盘方位|西南偏西]]，中心于{{lang|en|UTC}}下午15点从[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]以南约165公里海域经过。由于风切变增多，希梅纳继续减弱，于9月3日降级成热带低气压<ref name="nhc" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月5日早上6点，气旋穿过[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]<ref name="cphc" />，成为[[1999年太平洋飓风季|1999年]]的[[1999年飓风多拉|飓风多拉]]过后首场经过太平洋全部三大盆地的风暴<ref name="cphcb">{{cite report | author = Andy Nash | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimema report | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160528203051/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2003/jimena/jimena.php | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2003/jimena/jimena.php | archivedate = 2016-05-28 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。但在强烈风切变的影响下，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]监控低气压的时间很短，下层环流从中心暴露出来，到{{lang|en|UTC}}17点27分已近乎完全消散。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点，联合台风警报中心发布针对希梅纳的最后一份公告，宣布气旋在[[威克岛|威克岛]]东南方向约1151公里洋面完全消散<ref>{{cite report | author = Gary Padgett | year = 2003 | title = Monthly Global Tropical Cyclone Summary August 2003 | publisher = Australian Severe Weather | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322205555/http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/summ0308.htm | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | url = http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2004/summ0308.htm | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Jimena_(2003)_radar.GIF|left]]南侧经过的雷达图像]]

中太平洋飓风中心的[[气象学|气象学家]]于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月31日凌晨0点向[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷岛]]发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，并于次日凌晨3点发布热带风暴警告<ref name="cphc" />和山洪预警<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | year = 2003 | title = Hurricane Jimena, packing 100 mph winds, heads for Hawaii | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306152912/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-79099376.html | newspaper = The Columbian | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P1-79099376.html | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。面对预警和警告，当地居民把窗户封死并囤积应急物资<ref>{{cite news | author = KPUA | year = 2003 | title = Government officials and residents prepare for Hurricane Jimena | publisher = New West Broadcasting Corp. | accessdate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225716/http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=549 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=549 }}</ref>。随着风暴逼近，多个海滩被迫关闭，官员还把多种户外活动取消，以防万一<ref>{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Hurricane watch up for Hawaii | publisher = ''[[今日美国|USA Today]]'' | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | date = 2003-09-01 | archivedate = 2012-10-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020230045/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2003-08-31-hawaii-jimena_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/2003-08-31-hawaii-jimena_x.htm }}</ref>，[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]开设多个避难所并提供紧急服务<ref name="arc">{{cite news |author=KUPA |year=2003 |title=Big Island dodges hurricane threat |publisher=New West Broadcasting Corp. |accessdate=2016-09-01 |archivedate=2016-03-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225724/http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=553 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.kpua.net/news.php?id=553 }}</ref>。为了应对风暴来袭，美国红十字会共计耗费5000美元（2003年美元）<ref>{{cite news | author = Leila Fujimori | year = 2003 | title = Red Cross Hawaii needs own charity gifts | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308065535/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2003/10/29/news/story9.html | deadurl = no | newspaper = Honolulu Star-Bulletin | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2003/10/29/news/story9.html | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-08 }}</ref>。

逐渐减弱的热带风暴希梅纳从夏威夷州南侧经过，在多个岛上产生狂风暴雨。[[南端卡拉也|南角]]（{{lang|en|South Point}}）和[[卡胡拉威岛|卡胡拉威岛]]出现时速85至93公里的强烈阵风。<ref name="cphc" />[[檀香山|檀香山]]某气象站测得每小时58公里风速，[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]一间气象站所测风速为每小时35公里<ref name="cphcb" />。受风暴影响，夏威夷岛普遍出现152至254毫米降水<ref name="cphc" />。格伦伍德（{{lang|en|Glenwood}}）的降雨量有214毫米，这些降水有助于缓解夏威夷岛各地的旱情<ref name="rt">{{cite news | author = Rod Thompson | year = 2003 | title = Storm rain brings relief to parched Big Island | newspaper = Honolulu Star-Bulletin | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | url = http://archives.starbulletin.com/2003/09/02/news/story2.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307084052/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2003/09/02/news/story2.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-07 }}</ref>。夏威夷群岛沿海所测浪高范围在三至五米之间<ref name="cphc" />。

希梅纳产生的强风刮倒许多树木，还令供电线缆受损，导致1300居民家中停电<ref name="rt" />。风暴引发的暴雨还在夏威夷岛东侧引发轻度洪灾<ref>{{cite report | author = National Data Climatic Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Hawaii | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2008-06-04 | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~491403 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520012116/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~491403 | date =  }}</ref>。气旋激起的大浪和强烈的[[离岸流|离岸流]]对近海泳客的生命安全构成威胁，有350人获[[美国海岸警卫队|海岸警卫队]]、州警、地方警察、消防员及当地居民救援<ref>{{cite report | author = National Data Climatic Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Hawaii | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2008-06-04 | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~491402 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520012104/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~491402 | date =  }}</ref>。不过，整场风暴没有造成人员伤亡<ref name="nhc" />，其名称也没有在2004年春被[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]退役，之后又在[[2009年太平洋飓风季|2009年]][[2009年飓风希梅纳|继续使用]]<ref>{{cite report | author = John L. Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-01-29 | accessdate = 2016-09-01 | title = Hurricane Jimena Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132009_Jimena.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105644/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP132009_Jimena.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。

